thread.title: Mr Mike Higgs
thread.title_full: DoYouSpain.com evaluado por Mr Mike Higgs

author: Mr Mike Higgs
title: Mr Mike Higgs
text: used them a couple of times now. Prices are good and a reasonable range of vehicles. Need to watch for pricing on full to empty compared to full to full. There is some pressure with pop-ups for insurance. Overall will continue to use as service and prices are good. The car hire companies are also fair with returns and damage assessments.
